# Recordings: ignore everything except curated demo data that ships with the repo.
# User recordings should live in /mnt/rtsm-data/rtsm-recordings/ (bind-mounted from host),
# but this is a safety net in case someone uses a relative path like `--record recordings/foo`.
/recordings/*
!/recordings/session1/
!/recordings/demo_clip/
*.PRE_*

